OL,4,Cimportant pollinators
OL,6,FAsking local public spaces to plant
OL,7,Fwildflower meadows and leave grass
OL,8,Fverges alone will also encourage, and
OL,9,Fin turn protect, our bee population.
OL,11,FBees Feed Us
OL,13,FAlmost 90% of wild plants and 75% of
OL,14,Fleading global crops depend on animal
OL,15,Fpollination. 1 of every 3 mouthfuls of
OL,16,Four food depends on pollinators such
OL,17,Fas bees.
