OL,3,CWorld Bee Day: Celebrating the all-
OL,4,Cimportant pollinators
OL,6,FThe best thing to do if you see a bee
OL,7,Fstruggling is gently put it onto a bee-
OL,8,Ffriendly flower. If there are no bee-
OL,9,Ffriendly flowers around, mix 50/50
OL,10,Fwhite sugar and water to give the
OL,11,Fbumblebee a one-off energy boost,
OL,12,Fproviding the carbohydrates it needs
OL,13,Fto fly.
OL,15,FThey Rarely Sting
